 the efficiency of the fight has gone down the toilet since the half-tank is taking more damage than I would, has less HPs that I do making CH less efficient.  So now we're sitting out out butts at the end of a fight waiting on mana again.  Exactly the reason we group in the first place, to cut downtime to a minimum.  Of course, I'm just talking about single group fighting to say nothing of these new uber raids which I haven't even had the chance to experience.  The problem isn't that they are making changes, change can be good.  Making people re-evaluate their tactics is good.  However, completely re-writing the rules of the game throws everything out the window.  Here you spend all this time playing this character only to have your role changed to something you no longer find enjoyable.<br>
